---
layout: base
permalink: /store/
title: "E5 Enclave Store — Wear the Work. Fund the Future."
description: "Six sovereign collections — Restitution 246, House of Clubs, House of Spades, Celestial Court, Five-Gallon Sovereignty, Sovereign Menagerie. Every purchase funds Black community development in Liberty City, Miami."
breadcrumbs:
  - { label: "Store" }
extraJs:
  - "/assets/js/store.js"
---

<style>
/* ── STORE BASE ── */
.store-hero {
  padding: 80px 0 64px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vc-rule, #d4c5a0);
  background: var(--vc-bone, #fdfaf4);
}
.store-hero-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--vc-oxblood, #8b1a1a); margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.store-hero-h {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 62px);
  font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  max-width: 820px; margin: 0 0 20px; color: var(--vc-ink, #1a1614);
}
.store-hero-h em { font-style: italic; color: var(--vc-oxblood, #8b1a1a); }
.store-hero-deck {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.65;
  max-width: 600px; color: var(--vc-muted, #7a6a50); margin: 0;
}
.store-hero-meta {
  display: flex; gap: 32px; margin-top: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.store-hero-stat {
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--vc-muted, #7a6a50);
}
.store-hero-stat strong { display: block; font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 22px; color: var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a); font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 2px; }

/* ── COLLECTION NAV ── */
.store-collection-nav {
  position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 40;
  background: rgba(253,250,244,0.96);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vc-rule, #d4c5a0);
  padding: 0;
}
.store-collection-nav-inner {
  display: flex; gap: 0; overflow-x: auto;
  scrollbar-width: none;
  -ms-overflow-style: none;
}
.store-collection-nav-inner::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
.col-nav-btn {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  background: none; border: none;
  padding: 18px 24px;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 600; color: var(--vc-muted, #7a6a50);
  cursor: pointer;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  transition: color .2s, border-color .2s;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.col-nav-btn:hover { color: var(--vc-ink,#1a1614); }
.col-nav-btn.active {
  color: var(--vc-oxblood, #8b1a1a);
  border-bottom-color: var(--vc-oxblood, #8b1a1a);
}
.col-nav-btn[data-col="all"].active {
  color: var(--vc-ink,#1a1614);
  border-bottom-color: var(--vc-ink,#1a1614);
}

/* ── COLLECTION SECTION ── */
.store-collection {
  padding: 80px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vc-rule, #d4c5a0);
}
.store-col-head {
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}
.store-col-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 9.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--vc-oxblood, #8b1a1a); margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.store-col-h {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
  font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0 0 12px;
  color: var(--vc-ink,#1a1614);
}
.store-col-h em { font-style: italic; color: var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a); }
.store-col-tagline {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 15px; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--vc-muted,#7a6a50); margin: 0;
}
.store-col-campaign {
  display: inline-block; margin-top: 10px;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.32em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a);
  padding: 4px 10px; border: 1px solid var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a);
}

/* ── PRODUCT GRID ── */
.store-products-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 20px;
}
.product-card {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  background: var(--vc-bone, #fdfaf4);
  border: 1px solid var(--vc-rule, #d4c5a0);
  transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
  text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
}
.product-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}
.product-img-wrap {
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  background: #111;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
}
.product-img-wrap img {
  width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform .4s ease;
}
.product-card:hover .product-img-wrap img { transform: scale(1.04); }
.product-img-placeholder {
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); font-size: 14px;
  text-align: center; padding: 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0e0e0e 0%, #1a1410 100%);
}
.product-badge {
  position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 12px;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 8.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 3px 8px;
  background: var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a); color: #fff7e5;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.product-badge.limited { background: #d4a84b; color: #1a1407; }
.product-body {
  padding: 20px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;
  flex: 1;
}
.product-cat {
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.32em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--vc-muted,#7a6a50);
}
.product-name {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 17px; font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.2; color: var(--vc-ink,#1a1614); margin: 0;
}
.product-price {
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a); margin-top: 2px;
}
.product-impact {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 12px; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--vc-muted,#7a6a50); margin-top: 2px;
}
.product-add {
  margin: 12px 20px 20px;
  display: block;
  padding: 12px 0;
  background: var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a);
  color: #fff7e5;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 600; text-align: center;
  border: none; cursor: pointer;
  transition: background .2s;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.product-add:hover { background: #6e1515; }
.product-add.coming-soon {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--vc-muted,#7a6a50);
  border: 1px solid var(--vc-rule,#d4c5a0);
  cursor: default;
}

/* ── VENDOR STRIP ── */
.store-vendor-strip {
  padding: 48px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vc-rule,#d4c5a0);
  background: var(--vc-parchment, #f5ede0);
}
.store-vendor-rubric {
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.36em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a); margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.store-vendor-grid {
  display: flex; gap: 0; flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.store-vendor-item {
  flex: 1; min-width: 160px;
  padding: 20px 28px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--vc-rule,#d4c5a0);
}
.store-vendor-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
.store-vendor-name {
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--vc-ink,#1a1614); margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.store-vendor-role {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 13px; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--vc-muted,#7a6a50);
}

/* ── CART DRAWER ── */
.store-cart-toggle {
  position: fixed; bottom: 28px; right: 28px; z-index: 90;
  background: var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a);
  color: #fff7e5;
  border: none; cursor: pointer;
  width: 56px; height: 56px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(139,26,26,0.4);
  transition: background .2s, transform .2s;
}
.store-cart-toggle:hover { background: #6e1515; transform: scale(1.05); }
.store-cart-badge {
  position: absolute; top: -4px; right: -4px;
  width: 20px; height: 20px;
  background: #d4a84b; color: #1a1407;
  border-radius: 50%;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}
.store-cart-drawer {
  position: fixed; top: 0; right: -420px; bottom: 0;
  width: 420px; max-width: 100vw;
  background: var(--vc-bone,#fdfaf4);
  border-left: 1px solid var(--vc-rule,#d4c5a0);
  z-index: 200;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  transition: right .3s ease;
  box-shadow: -8px 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}
.store-cart-drawer.open { right: 0; }
.cart-drawer-head {
  padding: 24px 28px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vc-rule,#d4c5a0);
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
}
.cart-drawer-title {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--vc-ink,#1a1614);
}
.cart-drawer-close {
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 22px; color: var(--vc-muted,#7a6a50);
  line-height: 1; padding: 0;
}
.cart-drawer-items {
  flex: 1; overflow-y: auto;
  padding: 20px 28px;
}
.cart-empty {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 16px; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--vc-muted,#7a6a50); text-align: center;
  padding: 60px 0;
}
.cart-item {
  display: flex; gap: 16px; padding: 16px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vc-rule-2,#e8dfc8);
}
.cart-item-thumb {
  width: 64px; height: 64px; flex-shrink: 0;
  background: #111; object-fit: cover;
}
.cart-item-info { flex: 1; }
.cart-item-name {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--vc-ink,#1a1614); margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.cart-item-price {
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a);
}
.cart-item-remove {
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--vc-muted,#7a6a50); margin-top: 6px;
  padding: 0;
}
.cart-drawer-foot {
  padding: 20px 28px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--vc-rule,#d4c5a0);
}
.cart-subtotal {
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--vc-ink,#1a1614);
}
.cart-subtotal strong { font-size: 15px; }
.cart-checkout-btn {
  display: block; width: 100%;
  padding: 16px; text-align: center;
  background: var(--vc-oxblood,#8b1a1a); color: #fff7e5;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700;
  border: none; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
  transition: background .2s;
}
.cart-checkout-btn:hover { background: #6e1515; }
.cart-overlay {
  position: fixed; inset: 0;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
  z-index: 199;
  display: none;
}
.cart-overlay.open { display: block; }

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 1100px) { .store-products-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 800px) { .store-products-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 500px) { .store-products-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .store-cart-drawer { width: 100vw; } }
</style>

{# ── HERO ── #}
<section class="store-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="store-hero-eyebrow reveal">E5 Enclave Store</div>
    <h1 class="store-hero-h reveal">Wear it. <em>Fund the work.</em></h1>
    <p class="store-hero-deck reveal">Six sovereign collections. Every purchase routes revenue directly to founding programs — McCartney Academy, FarmBlock, Restitution 246, and the Black Dragons Initiative.</p>
    <div class="store-hero-meta reveal">
      <div class="store-hero-stat"><strong>6</strong>Collections</div>
      <div class="store-hero-stat"><strong>30+</strong>Items at launch</div>
      <div class="store-hero-stat"><strong>POD</strong>Ships to your door</div>
      <div class="store-hero-stat"><strong>~10%</strong>Revenue to programs</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── COLLECTION NAV ── #}
<nav class="store-collection-nav" aria-label="Collections">
  <div class="container store-collection-nav-inner">
    <button class="col-nav-btn active" data-col="all">All Collections</button>
    <button class="col-nav-btn" data-col="restitution-246">Restitution 246</button>
    <button class="col-nav-btn" data-col="house-of-clubs">House of Clubs</button>
    <button class="col-nav-btn" data-col="house-of-spades">House of Spades</button>
    <button class="col-nav-btn" data-col="celestial-court">Celestial Court</button>
    <button class="col-nav-btn" data-col="farmblock">Five-Gallon Sovereignty</button>
    <button class="col-nav-btn" data-col="menagerie">Sovereign Menagerie</button>
  </div>
</nav>

{# ── COLLECTION 1: RESTITUTION 246 ── #}
<section class="store-collection" data-collection="restitution-246" id="restitution-246">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="store-col-head reveal">
      <div class="store-col-eyebrow">Collection I — Restitution 246</div>
      <h2 class="store-col-h">The Restoration <em>Doctrine Capsule</em></h2>
      <p class="store-col-tagline">"Restoration is not a gesture. It is a settlement."</p>
      <span class="store-col-campaign">Record · Restore · Reckon</span>
    </div>
    <div class="store-products-grid" id="products-restitution-246">
      {% set r246 = [
        { slug: 'restoration-hoodie', name: 'Restoration Standard Hoodie', price: 95, cat: 'Apparel', badge: '', impact: '~$10 funds R246 legal research', img: '' },
        { slug: 'settlement-crew', name: 'Settlement Crew', price: 85, cat: 'Apparel', badge: '', impact: '~$9 funds R246 legal research', img: '' },
        { slug: 'ledger-tee', name: 'Ledger Tee', price: 55, cat: 'Apparel', badge: '', impact: '~$6 funds R246 legal research', img: '' },
        { slug: 'archive-tote', name: 'Archive Tote', price: 65, cat: 'Accessories', badge: '', impact: '~$7 funds R246 legal research', img: '' },
        { slug: 'doctrine-cap', name: 'Doctrine Cap', price: 45, cat: 'Accessories', badge: '', impact: '~$5 funds R246 legal research', img: '' }
      ] %}
      {% for p in r246 %}
      <article class="product-card reveal" data-product="{{ p.slug }}">
        <div class="product-img-wrap">
          {% if p.img %}<img src="{{ p.img }}" alt="{{ p.name }}" loading="lazy">{% else %}
          <div class="product-img-placeholder">{{ p.name }}</div>{% endif %}
          {% if p.badge %}<span class="product-badge {% if p.badge == 'Limited' %}limited{% endif %}">{{ p.badge }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="product-body">
          <span class="product-cat">{{ p.cat }}</span>
          <h3 class="product-name">{{ p.name }}</h3>
          <div class="product-price">${{ p.price }}</div>
          <span class="product-impact">{{ p.impact }}</span>
        </div>
        <button class="product-add" data-product-id="{{ p.slug }}" data-product-name="{{ p.name }}" data-product-price="{{ p.price }}">Add to Cart →</button>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── COLLECTION 2: HOUSE OF CLUBS ── #}
<section class="store-collection" data-collection="house-of-clubs" id="house-of-clubs">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="store-col-head reveal">
      <div class="store-col-eyebrow">Collection II — E5 Card Set</div>
      <h2 class="store-col-h">House of <em>Clubs</em></h2>
      <p class="store-col-tagline">"Power. Wisdom. Legacy."</p>
      <span class="store-col-campaign">Sovereign Line · Clubs Suit</span>
    </div>
    <div class="store-products-grid">
      {% set clubs = [
        { slug: 'clubs-hoodie', name: 'Oversized Heavyweight Hoodie', price: 120, cat: 'Apparel', badge: '', impact: '~$12 funds E5 programs', img: '' },
        { slug: 'clubs-tee', name: 'Graphic Tee', price: 65, cat: 'Apparel', badge: '', impact: '~$7 funds E5 programs', img: '' },
        { slug: 'clubs-bomber', name: 'Satin Bomber Jacket', price: 185, cat: 'Outerwear', badge: '', impact: '~$19 funds E5 programs', img: '' },
        { slug: 'clubs-scarf', name: 'Silk Scarf', price: 95, cat: 'Accessories', badge: 'Luxury', impact: '~$10 funds E5 programs', img: '' },
        { slug: 'clubs-tote', name: 'Archive Tote — Embossed', price: 85, cat: 'Accessories', badge: '', impact: '~$9 funds E5 programs', img: '' },
        { slug: 'clubs-deck', name: 'Collector Deck — Foil Box', price: 55, cat: 'Art', badge: '', impact: '~$6 funds E5 programs', img: '' }
      ] %}
      {% for p in clubs %}
      <article class="product-card reveal" data-product="{{ p.slug }}">
        <div class="product-img-wrap">
          <div class="product-img-placeholder">{{ p.name }}</div>
          {% if p.badge %}<span class="product-badge {% if p.badge == 'Limited' or p.badge == 'Luxury' %}limited{% endif %}">{{ p.badge }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="product-body">
          <span class="product-cat">{{ p.cat }}</span>
          <h3 class="product-name">{{ p.name }}</h3>
          <div class="product-price">${{ p.price }}</div>
          <span class="product-impact">{{ p.impact }}</span>
        </div>
        <button class="product-add coming-soon" disabled>Coming Soon</button>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── COLLECTION 3: HOUSE OF SPADES ── #}
<section class="store-collection" data-collection="house-of-spades" id="house-of-spades">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="store-col-head reveal">
      <div class="store-col-eyebrow">Collection III — E5 Sovereign Couture</div>
      <h2 class="store-col-h">House of <em>Spades</em></h2>
      <p class="store-col-tagline">"Power. Poise. Heritage."</p>
      <span class="store-col-campaign">Black American Sovereign Luxury</span>
    </div>
    <div class="store-products-grid">
      {% set spades = [
        { slug: 'spades-hoodie', name: 'Signature Hoodie', price: 110, cat: 'Apparel', badge: '', img: '' },
        { slug: 'spades-bomber', name: 'Sovereign Bomber', price: 195, cat: 'Outerwear', badge: '', img: '' },
        { slug: 'spades-tee', name: 'Crest Tee', price: 60, cat: 'Apparel', badge: '', img: '' },
        { slug: 'spades-outerwear', name: 'Royal Outerwear', price: 245, cat: 'Outerwear', badge: '', img: '' },
        { slug: 'spades-cap', name: 'Crown Cap', price: 50, cat: 'Accessories', badge: '', img: '' },
        { slug: 'spades-tote', name: 'Legacy Tote', price: 75, cat: 'Accessories', badge: '', img: '' },
        { slug: 'spades-print', name: 'Celestial Print 18×24"', price: 85, cat: 'Art & Prints', badge: '', img: '' },
        { slug: 'spades-earrings', name: 'House Earrings', price: 65, cat: 'Jewelry', badge: 'Luxury', img: '' }
      ] %}
      {% for p in spades %}
      <article class="product-card reveal" data-product="{{ p.slug }}">
        <div class="product-img-wrap">
          <div class="product-img-placeholder">{{ p.name }}</div>
          {% if p.badge %}<span class="product-badge limited">{{ p.badge }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="product-body">
          <span class="product-cat">{{ p.cat }}</span>
          <h3 class="product-name">{{ p.name }}</h3>
          <div class="product-price">${{ p.price }}</div>
          <span class="product-impact">~${{ (p.price * 0.1) | round }}  funds E5 programs</span>
        </div>
        <button class="product-add coming-soon" disabled>Coming Soon</button>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── COLLECTION 4: CELESTIAL COURT ── #}
<section class="store-collection" data-collection="celestial-court" id="celestial-court">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="store-col-head reveal">
      <div class="store-col-eyebrow">Collection IV — Donor Edition</div>
      <h2 class="store-col-h"><em>Celestial Court</em></h2>
      <p class="store-col-tagline">"A throne above. A court beyond. Power written in the stars."</p>
      <span class="store-col-campaign">Designed for Donors · Crafted for Legacy</span>
    </div>
    <div class="store-products-grid">
      {% set celestial = [
        { slug: 'celestial-bomber', name: 'Celestial Crown Bomber', price: 295, cat: 'Outerwear', badge: 'Numbered', img: '' },
        { slug: 'celestial-hoodie', name: 'Star Regalia Hoodie', price: 145, cat: 'Apparel', badge: 'Limited', img: '' },
        { slug: 'celestial-tee', name: 'Cosmic Queen Tee', price: 75, cat: 'Apparel', badge: 'Numbered', img: '' },
        { slug: 'celestial-scarf', name: 'Celestial Silk Scarf', price: 165, cat: 'Accessories', badge: 'Luxury', img: '' },
        { slug: 'celestial-deck', name: 'Premium Collector Deck', price: 125, cat: 'Collector', badge: 'Numbered', img: '' }
      ] %}
      {% for p in celestial %}
      <article class="product-card reveal" data-product="{{ p.slug }}">
